Bob is a client living in Varrock, just north of the Estate Agent's office, and is involved in the Mahogany Homes activity. He is one of the possible NPCs that the player can be tasked with helping.

Construction contracts[edit | edit source]

Bob is a possible client given to the player by Mahogany Homes, and may ask you to build the following furniture for them, depending on the type of contract that player chose:

Furniture Resources Experience
Large table 4 planks 90 192 288 448
Bookcase (1) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Bookcase (2) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Cabinet (1) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Cabinet (2) 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Grandfather Clock 1 plank 127.5 160 190 240
Wardrobe 2 planks 45 96 144 224
Drawers 2 planks 45 96 144 224

Dialogue[edit | edit source]

This article on an NPC has an associated dialogue page.
Click here for a transcript of possible conversations with this NPC.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Bob's house is the only one in the Mahogany Homes minigame with a piece of furniture that can change name depending on what material is used to build it, being the teak table in the middle of the ground floor.
